categories: Category:Jedi Masters of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Tu-Anh was a female Jedi Master who lived during the last years of the Galactic Republic. She perished on Utapau toward the end of the Clone Wars while investigating a Separatist conspiracy. Her body was discovered by the locals and shown to Jedi Generals Anakin Skywalker and Obi-Wan Kenobi.
The corpse of Tu-Anh first appeared in the unfinished Star Wars: The Clone Wars episode titled "A Death on Utapau."
